om-temperature-multiferroics-in-atom-thin-materials</guid></item><item><title>新兴计算生态系统：人工智能、量子、生物和化学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-emerging-computing-ecosystem-ai-quantum-biological-and-chemical</link><description>计算生态系统正在发生巨大变化。人工智能、量子计算、百亿亿级超级计算机、生物 DNA、化学和神经形态技术将改变世界。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-emerging-computing-ecosystem-ai-quantum-biological-and-chemical.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 01:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-emerging-computing-ecosystem-ai-quantum-biological-and-chemical</guid></item><item><title>我们可能永远无法理解现实</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/we-may-never-understand-reality</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 01:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/we-may-never-understand-reality</guid></item><item><title>全面代理经济的障碍是什么？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/what-are-the-obstacles-to-a-full-on-agentic-economy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/what-are-the-obstacles-to-a-full-on-agentic-economy</guid></item><item><title>根据国会提出的法案，科技公司必须支付人工智能数据中心的能源成本</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tech-companies-would-have-to-pay-ai-data-center-energy-costs-under-bill-moving-in-congress</link><description>众议院小组委员会可能会在周三推进立法，要求科技公司支付运营数据中心以支持人工智能的能源成本。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tech-companies-would-have-to-pay-ai-data-center-energy-costs-under-bill-moving-in-congress.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:40:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tech-companies-would-have-to-pay-ai-data-center-energy-costs-under-bill-moving-in-congress</guid></item><item><title>一家初创公司正在使用特殊聚合物来更好地帮助神经愈合</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-startup-is-using-special-polymers-to-better-help-nerves-heal</link><description>可生物降解的材料可以帮助改善手术后或与鳄梨相关的事故后的愈合。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-startup-is-using-special-polymers-to-better-help-nerves-heal.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-startup-is-using-special-polymers-to-better-help-nerves-heal</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局的冷原子实验室正在创造太空中最奇怪的物质形式之一</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/nasas-cold-atom-lab-is-creating-one-of-the-weirdest-forms-of-matter-in-space</link><description>美国宇航局升级后的冷原子实验室正在将国际空间站变成量子研究的前沿，创造出表现惊人的超冷物质。这些实验可以解锁有关宇宙的新发现，同时为太空和地球上强大的未来技术铺平道路。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nasas-cold-atom-lab-is-creating-one-of-the-weirdest-forms-of-matter-in-space.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/nasas-cold-atom-lab-is-creating-one-of-the-weirdest-forms-of-matter-in-space</guid></item><item><title>马可·桑蒂尼谈半人马座阿尔法星项目：理性乐观有很大的空间</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/marco-santini-on-the-alpha-centauri-project-there-is-a-lot-of-space-for-rational-optimism</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/marco-santini-on-the-alpha-centauri-project-there-is-a-lot-of-space-for-rational-optimism.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 23:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/marco-santini-on-the-alpha-centauri-project-there-is-a-lot-of-space-for-rational-optimism</guid></item></channel></rss>